ants are warmly and the banker is warmly and the guard in the bank is dubious, but thats fine, i think maybe 500 stacks more will get the guards to con warmly actually the guards outside neriak are indiff to me and guards inside are dubious. well any idiot can figure out that you need like 800pp to hand in all that wine, so ask yourself if its worth it, but it is kinda fun to be the GOD of neriak sowing newbies who never seen sow before... Also the wine quest doesnt ruin faction with others like killing halflings does, and you have to kill 800*20 halflings to get the same faction soo dont even go there you will ruin 4 factions for ever since the faction lost is about 17 times more than you gain with inner and outer guards.<br/><br/>All Hail NINDARA Wood elf druid on Bristlebane</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
